{"tid":147683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"王毅回應中興被罰:反對單邊制裁","createTime":"2017-03-08T04:49:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-08T06:22:42.000Z","uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eb83c0ac4b7fab29dd08f9c83e4b67329ef9535c","tid":147683,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T04:49:27.000Z","msg":"在記者會上，有美國媒體詢問面對美國新的貿易保護主義措施，中國將有何應對。外長王毅反問，是指今天早上關於中興(00763)的消息嗎？<br />\n<br />\n他說，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中國政府一貫反對外國政府對中國企業進行單邊制裁</span></strong>。同時，也一直要求中國企業在海外合法經營。中國政府的主管部門會繼續關注企業是否受到了公正對待。<br />\n<br />\n美國政府今早宣布，中興通訊被控對伊朗銷售美國科技，違反了美國出口管制法律，公司已同意認罪並支付8.92億美元罰款。<br />\n<br />\nSource : HKEJ<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個記者應該追問南韓果單落佢面 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99ed76e1ac66c1a8e09b7c767c0f2c0bcc3ac7c9","tid":147683,"uid":21896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T04:55:10.000Z","msg":"你咁沙塵咪制裁番佢囉"},{"pid":"e28e682ab9013306220872c26a52e41e0b51e743","tid":147683,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T05:10:45.000Z","msg":"罰蘋果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69cd0dcfce8563c35b77b5aa9d8affbc12b52201","tid":147683,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T05:12:30.000Z","msg":"南韓樂天呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab3efe9ad93a95a04b75e516e1353d11170f14e2","tid":147683,"uid":42364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T05:16:40.000Z","msg":"樂天超市大陸關4家店後 其他多家店也遭以消防檢查之名臨時查封<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/146200/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/146200/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"00aae8964d6